column5: Hey Guys,  The park doesn't officially open until the weekend but they are doing online reservations as of NOW.  If you want a site with Hydro you're best to book it ASAP!  Contact me if you need anything at all!  Cheers, Ryan
Sorry guys here's the link...  http://www.lprca.on.ca/  And Phone Number:  Call 519-875-2874 or 1-877-990-9934 to reserve a campsite or for more information.
